window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The war against the AI was won but a new threat is rising. </b></p> <p>Hank Spears is content with his life as a scrapper until he unearths an artificial intelligence who warns him of a grave threat to all life in the universe. Since AI has long been outlawed and anyone caught harboring one is imprisoned or executed, the two must go on the run, fleeing into the far reaches of space.</p> <p><b>They must avoid capture, all for the sake of those who would imprison them.</b></p> <p>Looking for help from old friends to fight new enemies, Hank must find a way to save himself so that he can save the universe.</p> <p><b>Can this simple scrapper become the hero the universe needs before it’s too late?</b></p> <p><i>Find out in Star Scrapper, the thrilling new science fiction series from USA Today Bestselling Author J.N. Chaney and Matthew A. Goodwin</i>.</p>"; 
